WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.500
AI is cool but can we just like stop progressing it?

2
00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:05.000
I think AI is doing great things.

3
00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:06.700
I feel optimistic about AI.

4
00:00:06.700 --> 00:00:11.100
You also definitely have to be careful about hallucinations and false information

5
00:00:11.100 --> 00:00:14.700
and kind of making sure you're not de-scaling your own skills

6
00:00:14.700 --> 00:00:16.300
and instead working to upscale it.

7
00:00:16.300 --> 00:00:20.400
It's really great that, for example, my parents can use AI

8
00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:23.200
to find any information they want in Vietnamese

9
00:00:23.200 --> 00:00:24.500
because they don't speak English that well.

10
00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:28.800
I think AI like gives us the opportunity

11
00:00:28.800 --> 00:00:30.500
to learn more about the universe.

12
00:00:30.500 --> 00:00:32.500
I think it's a really powerful technology

13
00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:36.200
so it has to be developed conscientiously and ethically.

